googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: David Nix
googleReviewsBySlug.json.text: Patrick came to the house twice.  One company told me I needed to spend $4000  to repair the issue.  Patrick corrected the issue for 460.  He is a honest guy.  I will use him again!
googleReviewsBySlug.json.title: Champion Plumbing And Remodeling

googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: Matt & Holli Hicks
googleReviewsBySlug.json.text: We had a septic back up on April 24th which was on a weekend. Patrick showed up when NO ONE else would, stayed at our home until he found us a restoration company that came the same day and a septic company that could pump the system. He then helped us navigate the insurance process, secured a contractor and made all the plumbing repairs. It's been a two month process and he has been there to help at a moment's notice every step of the way. We cannot recommend him strongly enough!  As long as he's in this business, he will get all of our plumbing business. Great guy with a strong work ethic and is a veteran as well!  We are so appreciative of his time and help. He goes over and beyond to serve his customers.
googleReviewsBySlug.json.title: Champion Plumbing And Remodeling

googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: Shari Kellogg
googleReviewsBySlug.json.text: Patrick with Champion was great! Professional and on time. Was also almost $200 less than others. I definitely have a new go to plumber!
googleReviewsBySlug.json.title: Champion Plumbing And Remodeling

googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: Janet Tatum
